  <brief_title>Anesthesia for Awake Fiberoptic Intubation</brief_title>
  <official_title>Anesthesia for Awake Fiberoptic Intubation in Patients With Cervical Instability - Comparison of Translaryngeal Injection and &quot;Spray as You go&quot;-Technique</official_title>
  <sponsors>
